gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Thunder 125, Bucks 107
gameRecap.excerpt: The Thunder defeated the Bucks, 125-107. Shai Gilgeous-Alexander (23 points, seven rebounds) and Chet Holmgren (22 points, nine rebounds, three blocks) led the Thunder as Aaron Wiggins added 19 points. Brook Lopez (18 points) and Khris Middleton (18 points, seven rebounds, and six assists) led the Bucks in the loss.
